<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <%- include('./partials/head') %>
    <title>About Us</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/aboutstyle.css">
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('./partials/nav') %>
    <header>
        <h1>About Our Website</h1>
    </header>
    <main>
        <section>
            <p>
                Welcome to <strong>InfoYour</strong>, the ultimate space for all fans who just can't stop thinking about their favorite characters! 
                Whether it's a hero you admire, a villain you love to hate, or a sidekick that made you laugh out loud, we've got you covered.
            </p>
            <p>
                Our platform is designed to help you share your thoughts, stories, and feelings about characters that left a mark on you. 
                Write your heart out, share your unique perspective, and explore blogs by others who are just as passionate as you are.
            </p>
        </section>
        <section>
            <h2>What Can You Do Here?</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Sign up to join our community of passionate fans.</li>
                <li>Write blogs about the characters that inspire, excite, or frustrate you.</li>
                <li>Engage in discussions by commenting on other users' blogs.</li>
                <li>Discover new perspectives and learn from fellow fans.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>
        <section>
            <h2>Why Join Us?</h2>
            <p>
                We believe every character has a story, and every fan has a voice. Let your voice be heard, 
                connect with others, and make this community your home for character-driven discussions.
            </p>
        </section>
        <section>
            <h2>Get Started</h2>
            <p>
                Sign in, start writing, and let the world know how you feel about the characters that mean the most to you.
                Remember, every opinion matters, and every story adds value. Let's build something amazing together!
            </p>
        </section>
    </main>
    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2025 Character Chronicles. All Rights Reserved.</p>
    </footer>
    <%- include('./partials/scripts') %>
</body>
</html>
